OL,3,CBBC boss says broadcaster has asked
OL,4,CHuw Edwards to return #200,000 salary
OL,6,FThe BBC Director General said he
OL,7,Fcannot see disgraced presenter Huw
OL,8,FEdwards working again for the
OL,9,Fcorporation, as ITV News'
OL,10,FCorrespondent John Ray reports
OL,12,FBBC Director-General Tim Davie says
OL,13,Fthe broadcaster has asked Huw Edwards
OL,14,Fto return his #200,000 salary after he
OL,15,Fwas given a six month suspended prison
OL,16,Fsentence on Monday for accessing
OL,17,Findecent images of children.
