OL,3,CBBC boss says broadcaster has asked
OL,4,CHuw Edwards to return #200,000 salary
OL,6,FSpeaking at the Royal Television
OL,7,FSociety (RTS) London conference, Mr
OL,8,FDavie said Edwards' crimes were
OL,9,F"appalling" and that the BBC's
OL,10,Freputation was impacted.
OL,12,F"There's no doubt that an affair like
OL,13,Fthis impacts our reputation, and I
OL,14,Fdon't know yet in terms of just the
OL,15,Fdirect impact on trust," he added.
OL,17,FWhen asked how the BBC was getting
OL,18,Fback Edwards' #200,000 salary, he
OL,19,Freplied: "We want the money back and
OL,20,Fwe've asked for it back, and we're
OL,21,Fwaiting to hear back."
