OL,6,FMr Davie was also asked why Edwards'
OL,7,Fpay continued after the BBC was made
OL,8,Faware of charges against the 63-year-
OL,9,Fold.
OL,11,FHe replied that "we decided that pay
OL,12,Fcontinues until someone is charged"
OL,13,Fand added: "I think it was the right
OL,14,Fdecision based on current policy."
