OL,3,CBBC boss says broadcaster has asked
OL,4,CHuw Edwards to return #200,000 salary
OL,6,FWhen asked Edwards would ever work for
OL,7,Fthe BBC again, Davie replied: "For
OL,8,Fobvious reasons, this man has has just
OL,9,Fbeen convicted of appalling crimes,
OL,10,Fand it's pretty straightforward in my
OL,11,Fmind that I can't see him working at
OL,12,Fthe BBC."
OL,14,F"What I would say is we track it very
OL,15,Fcarefully, we're very mindful that
OL,16,Fwith people, trust in the BBC is
OL,17,Fessential, and I hope we do the right
OL,18,Fthings," he said.
