OL,6,F"And in the end, I think people are
OL,7,Fsmart and they'll make their
OL,8,Fjudgments, and I'll see what we do,
OL,9,Fand I think overall, there's no doubt
OL,10,Fabout it, these things impact your
OL,11,Freputation, but you can maintain trust
OL,12,Fby doing the right thing."
OL,14,FThe BBC paid Edwards more than
OL,15,F#475,000 last year before he resigned
OL,16,Fand left the corporation following the
OL,17,Fexplicit photos furore.
